    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood from the species Catalpa bignonioides, lightweight with a fine grain. It is used for ornamental items and cabinetry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
